task.summary: Add of the ConvertUtils class that provides an "encode" method to convert a String into an array of bits according to this project's standard for transmission
Creation of a runnable class to perform blinking
Modifying the Blinking class to handle 2 strings (for the ssid and the password). Adding a countdown before the blinking starts.
Creation of the Blink_View class Move of all the blinking process from Blink_Activity to Blink_View Blink_View provides a "go()" function to start the process
Creation and of a Blink_State enumation to transfert datas We will now transfert a Blink_State array instead of a byte array
Creation of a static method in Blinking_Activity that return the intent needed to properly start the activity
